Import the Author Table

table.au.Rd

Imports the Author table from the database.

table.au(ver = "upd")

Arguments

ver

Version of the database. Default is upd, for the latest version.

Value

A data frame containing a list of Authors whose work has been included the database.

Examples

table.au()
